summary:
Made for Global Game Jam 2020 by: 

@SvavelstickaDev 
@autious 
@noxlof

"We Have Doom at Home" is a small-scale MBF21 project centered around small " house-themed " maps with low enemy count and fast completion times.

- 2048x2048 (playable area) maps;
- No more than 50 enemies(+15 co-op) per map;
- Maximum 15 minutes of gameplay;
- Custom "contemporary" mbf21 arsenal created by Matt Eldrydge;
